ometry ¬†and many of its symbols, then use that information to determine a course and relay it to a helmsman so that course can be steered. ¬†All of this work takes place in real-world scenarios aboard our tall ships. ¬†Each program participant will receive an interactive Student Logbook to aid their learning and track their progress.";s:10:"post_title";s:24:"TopSail S.T.E.M. Program";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:25:"topsail-s-t-e-a-m-program";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2015-01-28 16:13:09";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2015-01-28 16:13:09";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:3:"629";s:4:"guid";s:32:"http://198.1.99.216/?page_id=562";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:16;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"558";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"2";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2014-11-01 22:53:44";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2014-11-01 22:53:44";s:12:"post_content";s:3338:"<div class="contact-us-page">
